# Defense-in-depth: geo-builder's designer mode (--edit) can write real acquired data
# straight into public/ (see CLAUDE.md Hard Architecture Rules + scripts/clean_public.py).
# build.sh/build.cmd clean this before every build, but ignore it too so it can never
# get committed even if that cleanup step is skipped or forgotten.
public/areas/*/layers/
public/areas/*/*.csv
public/catalog.head.json
